pulltitle: Bug 1223403 - set Require Only App-Extension-Safe API to allow built …
pullsbody:
…framework to be included in app extensions

The current library does not have the Require Only App-Extension-Safe API build setting set to YES and this creates a dynamic framework that is not safe to use in App extensions. This patch sets it to yes to it can be used safely within an app extension.
pull_repo_desc: An implementation of OCaml's Deferred for Swift.
